The paper deals with a robust design problem for far-field line-of-sight (LOS) propagation channels, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a computational approach to handle probabilistic constraints, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY).
